{"tid":2055230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當你同身邊同齡既朋友比較","createTime":"2020-06-07T19:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T00:37:04.000Z","uid":134141,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"53d95609fb737b7dc1af1fc009770d465761c784","tid":2055230,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人會覺得自己步伐比佢地行得慢<br />\nd朋友可能已經有自己一門生意<br />\n或者為某一d事情努力緊甚至接近成功<br />\n<br />\n再望翻自己<br />\n自己人生冇咩目標<br />\n或者有目標嘗試過努力<br />\n但仍然好似原地踏步緊<br />\n慢慢再冇努力既動力<br />\n日子變到得過且過咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人有同感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"75803837b37112f7e65d036712d721f1966f0987","tid":2055230,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3c198bac1385e5f73f2f5decfa0d7220298463","tid":2055230,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75803837b37112f7e65d036712d721f1966f0987","tid":2055230,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:57:18.000Z","msg":"生活很苦 但你要甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d49f2fdeb7e54ee6b9ca68292d057b9e46ff079","tid":2055230,"uid":38077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf3c198bac1385e5f73f2f5decfa0d7220298463","tid":2055230,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75803837b37112f7e65d036712d721f1966f0987","tid":2055230,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:57:18.000Z","msg":"生活很苦 但你要甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2